&lt;p&gt;오늘은 엄마랑 아침에 인더매스삼덕 카페를 가서 크루키를 먹고 커피가 맛있었어서 커피 노트도 챙겨서 연구실에 출근했다 평소보다 평온한날이었다&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>초여름 부산</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/travel/daily11/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/travel/daily11/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="초여름-부산"&gt;
 초여름 부산
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%b4%88%ec%97%ac%eb%a6%84-%eb%b6%80%ec%82%b0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2025-05-20&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/93fca964-3a49-4583-95d6-06fcd2b8b647" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;간단하게 일상으로만 쓸려다가,,, 넘좋앗어서 그냥 따로 뺐다 ㅎㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/45c2787d-5287-404c-891c-af902157f1ca" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;다대포 할매집!! 문어삼합 / 냄비라면 / 올빚베리막걸리 시켯는데 다맛있었당 특히 딸기막걸리는 집에오니깐 또생각나서 사올걸 후회해따&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/be04631d-dc3c-44e7-91f5-8fd9bf103064" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;넘이뻤던바닷가&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/34f3bc01-73dd-4ee7-8b7b-8bc1aaa42b6b" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;길이사왓는데 넘맛있어서 막퍼먹은 케이크 ㅋㅋ 멜트인멜로우 검색해보니까 다른디저트도 다마싯을거같아서 또사먹을듯&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2fe0ff7b-b118-4c72-b6d8-e19c9f6574db" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;생레몬하이볼 첨먹어봣는데 주점에서파는하이볼 같음&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a3ef2bcb-a475-4a73-a336-1d5dec4d5da3" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;다음날&amp;hellip; 지수집엔 마싯는게 많다 일리커피가 네스프레소보다 훨배 맛있는거같음 다크원두인데 쓴맛이없고 향이 엄청 좋다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/60d09c0e-d782-40f1-9831-86c96bd8f79b" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>허허</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily4/</link><pubDate>Wed, 07 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily4/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="허허"&gt;
 허허
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ed%97%88%ed%97%88"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2025. 5. 7. 16:24&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ee81b691-ebdf-4f12-a76e-f7b31328031b" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ac396243-d3de-4988-9ca8-d67f0af714b4" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1260" height="1460" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ee2904da-0d75-4565-b215-60605892f7ab" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘비록위험할뻔한 날이었지만?? 오감자라는 완벽한 선택과 adsp공부 내던지고 고민영유튜브보기 라는 처방으로 잘 견디는중
집에가서 저녁 적당히만먹구 or 베이글먹구 운동까지만하면 완벽하다구 헬스티산것도 내일오니까 더할나위없지.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘상태&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;아침: 빵 2조각&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;점심: 엄마가 싸준 밥이랑 과일&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;저녁: 가벼운 저녁식사 or 베이글 1개&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;운동: 런닝머신 30분&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;완벽!!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>열시미충전하는 연휴</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 06 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily8/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="열시미충전하는-연휴"&gt;
